You can download torrent files made available from an RSS feed and convert them into a format suitable for your handheld device. 
Please don't use this if it is illegal where you are.
It requires:
mysql db(schema in the repos)
ffmpeg configured with the h264 libraries (http://www.webupd8.org/2010/04/script-to-automatically-download-and.html)
and a few python modules
